Class ChineseJointMM

java.lang.Object

      com.jgaap.languages.ChineseJointMM
All Implemented Interfaces:
Displayable, java.lang.Comparable<Language>
public class ChineseJointMM
extends Language

Representation of Chinese in jgaap using GB2123 and a joint matching technique for parsing it into words. Joint matching compares the results of forward matching and reverse matching and takes the more likely result.

Author:
Michael Ryan
